title: 'Held back when team needed more': Ex-India pacer questions Bumrah’s impact in England

description: Mohit Suri's 'Saiyaara,' starring Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda, has become a surprise romantic blockbuster, earning over Rs 300 crore in India. author: GAURAV TALWAR
description: A devastating flash flood in Dharali village was triggered by a massive collapse of glacial sedimentary deposits, not just heavy rain. Experts estimate an avalanche of 360 million cubic meters of debris flattened structures and claimed lives. The unstable glacial deposit, combined with steep terrain, accelerated the debris flow, leaving residents with no chance of escape.
title: Dharali flash flood: 360 million cubic metres of glacial debris came tumbling down, experts estimate

description: In Bhopal, a 22-year-old law student, Sanskar Babele, was fatally stabbed following a dispute at a petrol pump. title: Law student stabbed to death over jumping line at petrol pump
